*   [Matchbox Educable Noughts and Crosses Engine](/Matchbox_Educable_Noughts_and_Crosses_Engine), a much simpler, yet historically significant, learning machine.
*   [Samuel's learning computer checkers (draughts)](/Arthur_Samuel_(computer_scientist)), an early pioneer in machine learning applied to games.
*   [TD-Gammon](/TD-Gammon), a [backgammon](/Backgammon) neural network that demonstrated early success with reinforcement learning.
*   [Pluribus (poker bot)](/Pluribus_(poker_bot)), an AI that conquered multi-player no-limit poker.
*   [AlphaZero](/AlphaZero), the generalized successor to AlphaGo Zero, mastering multiple games.
*   [AlphaFold](/AlphaFold), a [DeepMind](/DeepMind) AI focused on protein folding, showing the breadth of AI application.